snippet.title: SimpleRockets [Official Trailer]
snippet.description:
SimpleRockets is available on iOS, Android, and PC. 
http://simplerockets.com

Check out the SimpleRockets forums to see awesome ship designs, picture albums, and videos of how people are playing the game:
http://www.reddit.com/r/simplerockets/

Music is Global Reach by 1M1 Music
Art by Matt Clair (http://mattclair.net/)

SimpleRockets is developed by Jundroo (http://jundroo.com).
